Mods:

+ Added Nether Chested (by Fuzs)
+ Added Stoneworks (by Fuzs)
+ Added Overflowing Bars (by Fuzs)

+ Added When Dungeons Arise - Loot Tweaks (by Aureljz)
+ Added Fabric Seasons: Terraformers Compat (by D4rkness_King)
+ Added Fabric Seasons: Delight Compat (by D4rkness_King)
+ Added Fabric Seasons: BYG Compat (by D4rkness_King)
+ Added Fabric Seasons: Extras (by D4rkness_King)
+ Added Bobby (by Johni0702)
+ Added Entity Collision FPS Fix Refabricated (by Corgi_Taco)
+ Added DEUF Refabricated (by ElocinDev)
+ Added Game window go brrr (by Zensonaton)
- Removed Extended Armor Bars Forked (Replaced)
- Removed Creatures From The Snow (Contains stolen assets, failed the vibe check)
- Removed Farsight (Replaced)
- Removed Smooth Boot (Replaced)

Configs:
- Blacklisted Basic Inventory Hoppers, Crystalline Flowers, and Enchanted Basins from being carried via CarryOn
- Minor quest tweaks, fixes, and additions

Updates:
- Added many new mobs, textures, items, and reworks (Oh The Biomes You'll Go)
- Added new blocks and connected textures to some blocks (Architect's Palette)
- Added new blocks (Every Compat)
- Added support for Meadow, Charm and Architect's Palette (Variant Crafting Tables)
- Added the Totem of Illusion and the Totem of Freezing (Friends & Foes)
- Added 2 new fish and 2 new blocks (Nether Depths Upgrade)
- Added the Gabbro geode (More Geodes)
- Added Mod Name sorting (Tom's Simple Storage)
- Added support for Deeper and Darker slabs (KleeSlabs)
- Added more entries to the default blacklist (Carry On)
- Removed/renamed all Aether related items (Paradise Lost)
- Renaming / repairing no longer accounts for the prior work penalty of an item (Easy Anvils) 
- The 'Too Expensive!' limit is now disabled (Easy Anvils)
- Right click harvesting now uses less hunger (RightClickHarvest) 
- Moved chat auto complete suggestions to accommodate for chat heads (Chat Heads)
- Tortoise/Alligator Eggs spawn much faster now (Naturalist)
- Summoning is no longer optional on recipes (Spirit)
- Ducks no longer lay Chicken Eggs (Naturalist)
- Dispensers can now deploy keys against key lockable blocks (Supplementaries)
- Many changes to the Frostologer boss (Frostiful)
- Destroyed unclaimed graves will now drop all its contents, or the grave containing the items, on the ground (You're In Grave Danger)
- Vanilla connection attempts on servers from bots will no longer appear in logs (Logs BeGone) 
- Fixed the Smithing Table having invalid icons and improved mod compatibility (Mandalas GUI)
- Fixed high memory usage (Diagonal Fences)
- Fixed issues with nbt data not spawning the mob correctly (Spirit)
- Fixed pedestals not storing data correctly (Spirit)
- Fixed anvils losing items after it has remained open when the anvil has just been damaged (Easy Anvils)
- Fixed the Zombie Villager version of the Chef and Cook missing textures (Chef's Delight)
- Fixed small animals trying to path-find through diagonal fence connections (Diagonal Fences)
- Fixed villagers not taking up the work of cooking with the skillet (Chef's Delight)
- Fixed a bug that caused Catfish to get stuck on top of water or in 1 deep areas (Naturalist)
- Fixed Bears getting stuck in their sleeping animation (Naturalist)
- Fixed Fireflies spawning en-masse (Naturalist)
- Fixed notice boards not working with banner patterns (Supplementaries)
- Fixed wind entities causing massive lag (Frostiful)
- Fixed Void Totems not working properly for void damage (Charm of Undying)
- Fixed Rotten Cherries not being compostable (Vinery)
- Fixed Apple Juice not depleting when drank (Vinery)
- Many fixes and improved performance (Fabric Seasons)
- Updated all mods
